-- collatz-step.cell: one step of the Collatz conjecture
-- Tests: conditional arithmetic, modular operation

ÔŐó check-even
  given n Ôëí 7
  yield is-even

  ÔŐó= is-even ÔćÉ n % 2 == 0

  ÔŐĘ is-even = false

ÔŐó collatz
  given n Ôëí 7
  given check-evenÔćĺis-even
  yield next

  ÔŐó= next ÔćÉ if check-evenÔćĺis-even then n / 2 else n * 3 + 1

  ÔŐĘ next = 22
